# Production environment template. Vite loads `.env.production` automatically
# during `vite build` (layered over `.env`), or set this as a real build-time
# environment variable on your deployment platform / in your Dockerfile.
#
# Missing this at build time isn't silently ignored: main.tsx checks
# `config.isConfigured` before rendering the app and shows a clear
# "Configuration error" screen instead of every API call failing with a
# cryptic network error.

VITE_API_URL=https://missionos-backend.onrender.com
